📝TUTORIAL : How to pump for Dummies ?

🖋 STEP 1 :
Be sure to sign up on Binance transfer funds. The transfer can take a while so be prepared and do it as soon as possible.

📢STEP 2 : 
When the coin is announced, in order to make the maximum of profits you have to buy as fast as possible. The price will rise up quickly, because all the WSB will want to buy the coin to the lowest price. 

💡STEP 3 : 
(Tips) Place your buy order a little bit more than the current price in order to be sure to buy the coin. If you place your buy order too low, you might not be able to buy the coin.(Be sure to NOT buy the coin too expensive, we can not control every buy orders so be prudent and do not take too much risk. Our goal is to make you w profits so DO NOT BE GREEDY!).

⚙️SCENARIO : 
Let's say the current price's coin is between 200sats and 208sats. If you place your buy order at 200sats, you can be pratically sure you will not be able to buy the coin. Demands will be strong and the price will naturally rise up. In the other side, if you place you buy order between 210sats and 215sats (even at 220-225sats the deal is pretty good), you will have better chance to buy the coin. 
You have to know that during a pump the coin's price can easily exceed 50% of his value, with an average of 80% (we already saw a pump with a growth about 400%)

💰STEP 4 : 
As soon as you order is completed, you need to place a sell order. We do not have the power to tell you when you should sell your coin, it's up to you and it depends which price did you get it. 
🚧Do not shit yourself and sell too early but also DO NOT place your sell order to high. If you place your order too high, you might not be able to sell. So be prudent and DO NOT BE GREEDY !🚧
Do your calcul, place your sell order and make profits, It's E-A-S-Y !

👏🏽STEP 5 : 
Share our Telegram to your friends, bigger we are, bigger profits you will get.
